Having experimented with numerous relish and compotes that were good but not exciting, I discovered this one. Fabulous! It received rave reviews not only this Thanksgiving but last night as an accompaniment to brisket & latkes. The only change I made was instead of using water, I added more white wine with the cranberries. I had some inexpensive white wine and it worked perfectly.

