Rating: 4
We have made this wonderful cranberry recipe at Thanksgiving every year since it appeared in Gourmet in 1995. It is my favourite item in our Thanksgiving menu. When I can't get the dried sour cherries, I substitute dried sweet cherries and cut the sugar just a little with good results. Try to get small shallots!

